<lb n="0564c24"/><head>No. 748</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0564c25"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>佛說護淨經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0564c26"/>
<lb n="0564c27"/><byline type="Translator">失譯<note n="0564013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【宋】【元】【宮】，人＋（名）【明】</note><app n="0564013"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">人名</rdg></app>今附東晉錄</byline>
<lb n="0564c28"/><p><note n="0564014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">往昔佛＝佛往昔【三】【宮】</note><note n="0564014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">往昔佛＝佛往昔【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0564014"><lem>往昔佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛往昔</rdg></app>共阿難行。遇值一池。東西四十里。
<lb n="0564c29"/>南北四十里。深四十里。池中有虫。其<note n="0564015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔形〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0564015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔形〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0564015"><lem>形</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>似
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0748.0565a" n="0565a"/>
<lb n="0565a01"/><note n="0565001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">科＝蝌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">科＝蝌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565001"><lem>科</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">蝌</rdg></app>蚪形黑如墨。佛語阿難。識此<note n="0565002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔池中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔池中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565002"><lem>池中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>虫不。
<lb n="0565a02"/>答言不識。佛語阿難。此池中虫者。十方世界
<lb n="0565a03"/><note n="0565003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝本【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大＝本【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565003"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">本</rdg></app>眾僧。食不淨食。墮此臭穢糞屎池中。常
<lb n="0565a04"/>食不淨。五百萬世中受此苦惱竟。<note n="0565004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後＋（復）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後＋（復）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565004"><lem>後</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">後復</rdg></app>五百世
<lb n="0565a05"/>中<note n="0565005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔復〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565005"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>墮餓狗中。常食不淨。<note n="0565006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝後【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復＝後【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565006"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">後</rdg></app>墮&CB00337;中。五百
<lb n="0565a06"/><note n="0565007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＋（中復）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＋（中復）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565007"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">世中復</rdg></app>常食不淨。復墮蜣<note n="0565008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜋＋（蟲）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蜋＋（蟲）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565008"><lem>蜋</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">蜋蟲</rdg></app>中常食不淨。亦五
<lb n="0565a07"/>百世<note n="0565009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝復【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得＝復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565009"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>出為人。常生貧窮<note n="0565010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">家＋（中）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">家＋（中）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565010"><lem>家</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">家中</rdg></app>。衣不覆形。食
<lb n="0565a08"/>不充口。常<note n="0565011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（&CB13542;&CB01972;）【宋】【宮】，（&CB13540;&CB01972;）【元】，（籺糕）【明】</note><app n="0565011"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食&CB13542;&CB01972;</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">食&CB13540;&CB01972;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">食籺糕</rdg></app>糠<note n="0565012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝餅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝餅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565012"><lem>飯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">餅</rdg></app>。&M010527;飢不足。佛語諸比丘。
<lb n="0565a09"/>有如是<note n="0565013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【宮】</note><app n="0565013"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。受罪尤苦。無量無邊。<note n="0565014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誡＝戒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誡＝戒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565014"><lem>誡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">戒</rdg></app>語後世
<lb n="0565a10"/>末法中諸比丘。不可不慎。一切眾僧。有住止
<lb n="0565a11"/>處。作不淨食。不足<note n="0565015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">往＝住【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">往＝住【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565015"><lem>往</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>食。欲<note n="0565016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨＝得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565016"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>食者。一切白
<lb n="0565a12"/>衣食。如法著衣持&CB00425;。<note n="0565017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">稱＝攝【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稱＝攝【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565017"><lem>稱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">攝</rdg></app>四威儀。如法往造。
<lb n="0565a13"/><note n="0565018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乞〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔乞〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565018"><lem>乞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>是真比丘。除其邪命。<note n="0565019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如法活命＝活命如法【宮】</note><app n="0565019"><lem>如法活命</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">活命如法</rdg></app>。佛不妄
<lb n="0565a14"/><note n="0565020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝語【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝語【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565020"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">語</rdg></app>。福報如影響。往昔比丘。<note n="0565021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">新＝報【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">新＝報【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565021"><lem>新</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">報</rdg></app>得阿羅<note n="0565022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漢＋（果）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">漢＋（果）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565022"><lem>漢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">漢果</rdg></app>
<lb n="0565a15"/>有結業身有便利患。<note n="0565023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＝向【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜＝向【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565023"><lem>夜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">向</rdg></app>闇上廁。見一比丘。
<lb n="0565a16"/>在廁邊呻吟。阿羅漢語是比丘。汝本好用<note n="0565024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝行【宮】</note><app n="0565024"><lem>意</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">行</rdg></app>
<lb n="0565a17"/>人。云何墮餓鬼中。呻吟如是。餓鬼比丘答言。
<lb n="0565a18"/>我<note n="0565025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餓＝饑【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餓＝饑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565025"><lem>餓</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">饑</rdg></app>渴來久。五百餘年。不見漿<note n="0565026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔水〕－【宮】</note><app n="0565026"><lem>水</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。正欲趣
<lb n="0565a19"/>廁<note n="0565027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">用＝欲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">用＝欲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565027"><lem>用</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">欲</rdg></app>食不淨。護廁鬼<note n="0565028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神＋（手捉）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神＋（手捉）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565028"><lem>神</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">神手捉</rdg></app>。鐵杖打我。不得近
<lb n="0565a20"/>廁。憶念本曾作比丘。知<note n="0565029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">僧＝淨【宋】【元】【宮】，僧＋（淨）【明】</note><app n="0565029"><lem>僧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">淨</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">僧淨</rdg></app>事<note n="0565030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝&unrec;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時＝&unrec;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565030"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&unrec;</rdg></app>。是<note n="0565031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">用＋（是）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">用＋（是）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565031"><lem>用</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">用是</rdg></app>觸
<lb n="0565a21"/>眾僧淨。<note n="0565032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔食〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔食〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565032"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>以不淨食<note n="0565033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＝飴【三】</note><note n="0565033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＝飴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0565033"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">飴</rdg></app>眾僧。故致此殃遇
<lb n="0565a22"/>值阿羅漢善知識。阿羅漢。為比丘<note n="0565034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">僧＝眾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">僧＝眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565034"><lem>僧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">眾</rdg></app>中。燒
<lb n="0565a23"/>香&CB00057;願。即免餓鬼。還復人道。<note n="0565035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＝誡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛＝誡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565035"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">誡</rdg></app>語諸比丘。
<lb n="0565a24"/>不可不慎。一切不得觸眾僧淨食。佛不虛言。
<lb n="0565a25"/>福報如影響。十八地獄經中出罪福。此餓鬼
<lb n="0565a26"/><note n="0565036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔本〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔本〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565036"><lem>本</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>從人道中來。以不清淨手。觸眾僧淨器。
<lb n="0565a27"/>以不<note n="0565037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨手＝清淨手自【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨手＝清淨手自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565037"><lem>淨手</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">清淨手自</rdg></app>。觸沙門淨食。以不<note n="0565038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（清）＋淨【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0565038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（清）＋淨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0565038"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">清淨</rdg></app>食。著沙門
<lb n="0565a28"/>淨食中。以不淨食。<note n="0565039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＝飼【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0565039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＝飼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0565039"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飼</rdg></app>眾僧故。後五百世中。
<lb n="0565a29"/>墮餓鬼中。常食不淨。欲趣廁上<note n="0565040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食糞＝噉糞屎【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食糞＝噉糞屎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565040"><lem>食糞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">噉糞屎</rdg></app>于時廁
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0748.0565b" n="0565b"/>
<lb n="0565b01"/>神。手捉鐵杖打<note n="0565041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（之令…膿血））十一字＝（（餓鬼不得近廁此餓鬼常食膿血食人））十五字【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（之令…膿血））十一字＝（（餓鬼不得近廁此餓鬼常食膿血食人））十五字【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565041" word-count="11"><lem>之。令不得近。此鬼食人膿
<lb n="0565b02"/>血</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">餓鬼不得近廁此餓鬼常食膿血食人</rdg></app>。涕唾及蕩<note n="0565042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滌＝除【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滌＝除【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565042"><lem>滌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">除</rdg></app>惡汁。常<note n="0565043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">伺＝守【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">伺＝守【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565043"><lem>伺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">守</rdg></app>捕婦女<note n="0565044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">產＋（藏）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">產＋（藏）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565044"><lem>產</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">產藏</rdg></app>血不
<lb n="0565b03"/>淨。以為飲食。復經<note n="0565045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">五百＋（萬）【宮】</note><app n="0565045"><lem>五百</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">五百萬</rdg></app>世。墮&CB00337;狗蜣蜋<note n="0565046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565046"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0565b04"/>中。常食臭<note n="0565047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">糞＋（穢）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">糞＋（穢）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565047"><lem>糞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">糞穢</rdg></app>不淨。受斯苦<note n="0565048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">劇＋（之中）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">劇＋（之中）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565048"><lem>劇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">劇之中</rdg></app>。累世<note n="0565049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如此於百千＝勤苦數千萬【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如此於百千＝勤苦數千萬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565049"><lem>如此。
<lb n="0565b05"/>於百千</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">勤苦數千萬</rdg></app>劫。無有出期。難得解脫。痛不可言。
<lb n="0565b06"/>以不淨手觸男根。<note n="0565050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＋（手）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或＋（手）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565050"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">或手</rdg></app>觸女根。觸沙門淨器。
<lb n="0565b07"/><note n="0565051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以手）＋觸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（以手）＋觸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565051"><lem>觸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">以手觸</rdg></app>沙門淨食。以不淨食。著沙門淨食中。以
<lb n="0565b08"/>不淨食。<app type="＊" source="0565039"><lem>食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飼</rdg></app>眾僧故。致此殃。一切人肉眼不
<lb n="0565b09"/>知罪福。自今<note n="0565052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0565052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0565052"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>後。欲得福祐。佐眾僧作食。
<lb n="0565b10"/>以清淨手。捉眾僧淨器。<app type="＊" source="0565038"><lem>淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">清淨</rdg></app>手<note n="0565053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淘＝濤【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0565053"><lem>淘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">濤</rdg></app>米。<note n="0565054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">及＝乃【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及＝乃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565054"><lem>及</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">乃</rdg></app>以
<lb n="0565b11"/>淨米。著眾僧淨食中<note n="0565055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565055"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得福無量。自今<app type="＊" source="0565052"><lem>以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>
<lb n="0565b12"/>後。以此為常。一切眾人。普使聞<note n="0565056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">知＋（至心奉行）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">知＋（至心奉行）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565056"><lem>知</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">知至心奉行</rdg></app>。<note n="0565057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一切…響〕二百四十六字－【宮】</note><app n="0565057" word-count="246"><lem>一切檀
<lb n="0565b13"/>越。施設法會。供齋調度。持齋者得食。不持齋
<lb n="0565b14"/>者不得食。此飯一日持齋。得六十萬世餘糧。
<lb n="0565b15"/>不持齋者。六十萬世。墮餓鬼中。何以故。此信
<lb n="0565b16"/>施難銷。故寧吞熱鐵丸。不食此飯。吞熱鐵丸。
<lb n="0565b17"/>須臾間耳。食<note n="0565058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此〕－【三】</note><note n="0565058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0565058"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>信施。久受大苦。五百萬世
<lb n="0565b18"/>中。受餓鬼苦。諸有設食之處。一切如法作齋。
<lb n="0565b19"/>不得懷挾餘殘食。歸給妻子。若食此飯。若腋
<lb n="0565b20"/>底挾擔。後五百<note n="0565059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0565059"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。常挾熱鐵輪。左腋底入。
<lb n="0565b21"/>從右腋底出。一切齋飯。不可不慎。一米化作
<lb n="0565b22"/>熱丸。一切賢者。施設福會。於先嘗啜此食。都
<lb n="0565b23"/>作殘食。唐作此會。不如不作。何以故。諸天不
<lb n="0565b24"/>歡。鬼神不喜。此人於先&CB00573;者。亦五百世中。受
<lb n="0565b25"/>餓鬼苦。自今已後。欲得福者。如法作齋食。可
<lb n="0565b26"/>得福德。諸天歡喜。百神慶悅。天神擁護。經不
<lb n="0565b27"/>虛言。福報如影響</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
